Enum DocumentSelection.SelectionType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<DocumentSelection.SelectionType>
      • com.hcl.domino.data.DocumentSelection.SelectionType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<DocumentSelection.SelectionType>
    Enclosing interface:
    DocumentSelection

    public static enum DocumentSelection.SelectionType
extends Enum<DocumentSelection.SelectionType>
    The available document types that can be selected via DocumentSelection.select(Collection) and DocumentSelection.select(SelectionType...).
